{"date":"2017-06-21","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/45/fa/229018_GNQCN.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/45/fa/229018_GNQCN.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/45/fa/229018_GNQCN.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/45/fa/229018_GNQCN.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/45/fa/229018_GNQCN.jpg"},"summary":"谁要是以为村里太平安详那TA就大错特错了，因为村子里有一群异常欢脱的动物们。一只狐狸被误认为一只母鸡，一只和白鹳纠缠不清的兔子，还有一门想取代圣诞老人的鸭子。你们打算来度假吗？嗯，路过别停，直接开走吧…… \r\n面对一只傻兔子，一头园丁猪，一只懒狗和一只有性格障碍的母鸡，一只慈悲为怀的狐狸试着在这群动物中维护自己的伟大捕猎者形象。可它那些招儿总不见效，因此它想到了一条新路子：没错！那就是偷鸡蛋，孵小鸡儿，吓唬它们，再把它们吃掉。可这个宏大的计划没能迎来曙光，因为坏狐狸居然发现对这帮小家伙有了一丝叫做母爱的情感…… \r\n《艾特熊和赛娜鼠》的导演本杰明·雷内联手摄影导演、录音师、动画导演Patrick Imbert，将自己笔下的坏狐狸绘本故事搬上大荧幕。影片由Studio Canal 出品。","name":"Le Grand Méchant Renard et autres contes","name_cn":"大坏狐狸的故事","tags":[{"name":"剧场版","count":46,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":38,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2017","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"童话","count":27,"total_cont":0},{"name":"搞笑","count":20,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画电影","count":14,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动物","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"电影","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"PatrickImbert","count":5,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧情","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"法国动画","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"BenjaminRenner","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"7WA","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"非日本動畫電影","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"US","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"10","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"喜剧","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"治愈","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Film","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"部","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"大坏狐狸的故事"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"2017年6月21日"},{"key":"片长","value":"83分钟"},{"key":"导演","value":"Patrick Imbert / Benjamin Renner"},{"key":"编剧","value":"Jean Regnaud / Benjamin Renner"},